<p>Hi <%= @resource.email %>!</p>

<p>You, or someone who thinks they are you, requested a link to change your password. You can click the link below to change your password if you want to.</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, :reset_password_token => @token) %></p>
<p>Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>

<p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email and have a great day.</p>

